The draw for the Copa del Rey round of 8 has been released. The draw was released at the headquarters of the Royal Spanish Football Federation on Friday in Spain. The one legged fixture will take place on 4 February. Real Madrid were paired with Real Sociedad, while Barcelona will tackle Athletic Bilbao. Below is the Copa del Rey last 8 draw in full: Real Madrid vs Real Sociedad Athletic Bilbao vs Barcelona Mirandes vs Villarreal Granada vs Valencia The Copa del Rey final will be played on 18 April.